    <section class="wrapper intro fadeMe">

        <article class="">

            <h2>Customer Led Communication</h2>

            <!--                <em><span style="font-size:40px;">"</span>Customer Led Communication<span style="font-size:40px;">"</span></em>-->

            <p>Planning, creating and delivering both printed and digital communication, DST engages with every UK household at least once a week on behalf of some of the biggest and most influential global brands.</p>

            <p>We see ourselves as an extension of your business; embracing integrity and high standards to deliver a seamless and engaging communication experience.</p>





        </article>

        <div class="clear"></div>


    </section>

</section>



<section class="wrapper solutions fadeMe approach">

    <h2 class="title"><a name="home" class="anchor"></a>Our Approach</h2>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="solution_1">

            <div class="icon">
                <img src="/images/icon_plan.png" style="width: 30%; margin-left: 5%;">
            </div>

            <div class="text">
                <h3>Plan</h3>
                <p>
                    Understanding what your customers look like and what motivates them to engage, buy or respond to you is key to any successful customer engagement.
                </p>

                <p>Ensuring  you have the up-to-date capabilities to reach out and engage will help ensure a better long-term customer relationship.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="solution 1">

            <div class="icon">
                <img src="/images/icon_create.png" style="width: 20%;">
            </div>

            <div class="text">
                <h3>Create</h3>
                <p>
                    The increasingly sophisticated and demanding customer expects to receive the information they want, when they want it, by the channels they prefer, whether print or digital.
                </p>

                <p>Segmentation, generating individualised content and quality production can help you be more relevant to your customer.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="solution_3">

            <div class="icon">
                <img src="/images/icon_deliver.png" style="width: 34%;">
            </div>

            <div class="text">
                <h3>Deliver</h3>
                <p>
                    How and when you deliver your message can be the difference between treating everyone the same and engaging with people at a true one-to-one level.
                </p>
                <p>Actionable MI will provide you with knowledge about process and engagement levels to keep your communication improving.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>

</section>

