<section class="container grey ">


    <section class="wrapper solutions key_offerings core_services fadeMe">

        <h2 class="title"><a name="services" class="anchor"></a>Core Services</h2>

        <div class="content" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">

            <div class="intro">

                <p>Having created and sent tens of billions of communications across all print and digital channels, we can provide you with mature, efficient and empowering solutions.</p>
                <p>We use our global talent and resources to develop customised solutions for your organisation, optimising data and making it easy for you to send every single message according to the most appropriate channel or customer preference.</p>


            </div>



            <div class="core_box">


                <img src="/images/web_icons/data_management_v2.png">
                <strong>DATA</strong>
                <p>We design, build and manage databases, using this combination to acquire, understand and then transform raw data into competitive advantage.</p>
                <p>Consolidating data from disparate sources, we deliver integrated, intelligent infrastructures, using a single customer view to drive effective marketing across multiple channels.</p>

            </div>

            <div class="core_box">

                <img src="/images/web_icons/Consulting_insight.png">
                <strong>INSIGHT</strong>
                <p>DST has extensive experience in supporting CRM and customer projects, building solutions, planning and implementing programmes that add customer value and build ROI.</p>
                <p>We're highly skilled with data analytics and statistical modelling, generating new opportunities to increase communications efficiency and effectiveness.</p>

            </div>


            <div class="core_box">

                <img src="/images/web_icons/Print.png">
                <strong>PRINT</strong>
                <p>We combine our unparalleled breadth, depth and sophistication of manufacturing capabilities with the best new and niche services the market has to offer.</p>
                <p>We drive cost out of your print communications whilst delivering real performance and quality improvements.</p>

            </div>

            <div class="core_box">

                <img src="/images/web_icons/Email.png">
                <strong>EMAIL</strong>
                <p>Our broadcast and triggered email solutions are geared to drive your digitisation strategies regardless of your starting point.</p>
                <p>We put the right digital specialists and systems together to integrate email and print at the heart of your communications world.</p>

            </div>

            <div class="core_box">

                <p>
                    <img src="/images/web_icons/SMS.png">
                    <strong>SMS</strong>
                <p>Reach your customer’s pocket with timely and convenient information and customer service updates.</p>
                <p>
                    Our enterprise SMS solutions help you evolve triggered communications to improve customer journeys and motivate best next steps.
                </p>

            </div>


            <div class="core_box">

                <img src="/images/web_icons/Interactive.png">
                <strong>INTERACTIVE</strong>
                <p>DST's innovative interactive solutions let you use your existing assets to deliver multi-layered, interactive and tailored content instead of static communications.</p>
                <p>Give your customer the ability to drill down into their statement, bill or other communication to discover further information, greater understanding and relevant next steps.</p>

            </div>





            <div class="core_box">


                <img src="/images/web_icons/Video.png">
                <strong>VIDEO</strong>
                <p>Gain easy access to this emerging channel through DST’s video solutions which are integrated into our digital and print delivery platforms.</p>
                <p>Send personalised and tailored videos that engage, explain and drive meaningful customer experience.</p>


            </div>




            <div class="core_box">

                <img src="/images/web_icons/fulfilment.png">
                <strong>FULFILMENT</strong>
                <p>Handling your customers’ orders, responses, returns and enquiries, DST provides full end-to-end campaign solutions.</p>
                <p>
                    Our specialist response handling unit can handle calls, postal and online submissions fulfilling orders from our managed stock warehouse, plus printing on demand.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="clear"></div>




        </div>

        <div class="clear"></div>

    </section>

